OL,6,FIn 1995, he bought the franchise for
OL,7,Fthe American football team the Tampa
OL,8,FBay Buccaneers for a then record $192
OL,9,Fmillion. The club saw initial success,
OL,10,Fwinning the Super Bowl in 2002.
